---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="vibedecoding.io - AI Base Software Development">
	<header class="header">
		<nav class="nav">
			<a href="/" class="logo"><span class="prompt">❯</span> vibedecoding.io</a>
			<div class="nav-links">
				<a href="#pillars">[PILLARS]</a>
				<a href="#path">[PATH]</a>
				<a href="#why">[WHY]</a>
			</div>
		</nav>
	</header>

	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<div class="hero-badge">// THE PRAGMATIC ENGINEER'S GUIDE</div>
				<h1>The <span class="gradient-text">AI Base Development</span> Field Guide</h1>
				<p class="hero-subtitle">Not prompts. Not chat. Here's how you actually build with AI — from running models locally to deploying AI-native applications.</p>
				<div class="hero-cta">
					<a href="#pillars" class="btn btn-primary">$ EXPLORE</a>
					<a href="https://github.com/irbull/ai-the-hard-way" class="btn btn-secondary">./START_FUNDAMENTALS</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-visual">
				<div class="terminal">
					<div class="terminal-header">
						<span class="terminal-dots">● ● ●</span>
						<span class="terminal-title">~/ai-base-dev</span>
					</div>
					<div class="terminal-body">
						<div class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">❯</span> llms-the-hard-way/</div>
						<div class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">❯</span> fine-tuning/</div>
						<div class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">❯</span> inference-harness/</div>
						<div class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">❯</span> crucible/</div>
						<div class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">❯</span> dev-tools/</div>
						<div class="terminal-cursor">█</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="pillars" class="section pillars">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<span class="section-label">> SECTION_01</span>
					<h2>THE 5 PILLARS</h2>
				</div>
				<p class="section-intro">Five areas of hands-on experience that give you real depth in AI development.</p>
				
				<div class="pillars-grid">
					<div class="pillar-card">
						<div class="pillar-header">
							<span class="pillar-number">[01]</span>
							<h3>LLMs the Hard Way</h3>
						</div>
						<p>Build your understanding from first principles. No black boxes — learn how transformers actually work by building them.</p>
						<div class="pillar-links">
							<a href="https://github.com/irbull/ai-the-hard-way">→ VIEW TUTORIAL</a>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="pillar-card">
						<div class="pillar-header">
							<span class="pillar-number">[02]</span>
							<h3>Model Fine Tuning</h3>
						</div>
						<p>Take base models and specialize them for your use case. Used axolotl to fine tune models for specific tasks.</p>
						<div class="pillar-tags">
							<span class="tag">axolotl</span>
							<span class="tag">LoRA</span>
							<span class="tag">QLoRA</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="pillar-card">
						<div class="pillar-header">
							<span class="pillar-number">[03]</span>
							<h3>Inference Harness</h3>
						</div>
						<p>Run models locally with llama.cpp. Build your own inference layer on top for custom applications.</p>
						<div class="pillar-links">
							<a href="https://ianbull.com/posts/llamas-and-dinosaurs">→ READ POST</a>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="pillar-card">
						<div class="pillar-header">
							<span class="pillar-number">[04]</span>
							<h3>Custom Agents</h3>
						</div>
						<p>Built Crucible — a Firecracker-based agent framework. Understand why context engineering matters at scale.</p>
						<div class="pillar-links">
							<a href="https://github.com/irbull/crucible">→ EXPLORE CRUCIBLE</a>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="pillar-card">
						<div class="pillar-header">
							<span class="pillar-number">[05]</span>
							<h3>Developer Tools</h3>
						</div>
						<p>Built and deployed internal AI tools — Risk Analysis and Code Review. These are AI-native apps, not slash commands.</p>
						<div class="pillar-tags">
							<span class="tag">CODE REVIEW</span>
							<span class="tag">RISK ANALYSIS</span>
							<span class="tag">AI-NATIVE</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="path" class="section path">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<span class="section-label">> SECTION_02</span>
					<h2>THE LEARNING PATH</h2>
				</div>
				<p class="section-intro">A pragmatic journey from fundamentals to shipping real products.</p>
				
				<div class="path-flow">
					<div class="path-step">
						<div class="step-icon">📚</div>
						<h3>01 // LEARN</h3>
						<p>Start with LLMs the Hard Way. Understand transformers, tokenization, attention. Build the mental model.</p>
						<div class="step-resources">
							<span class="resource-link">→ ai-the-hard-way</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="path-arrow">→</div>

					<div class="path-step">
						<div class="step-icon">🔧</div>
						<h3>02 // TAME</h3>
						<p>Run models locally. Fine tune for your use case. Learn inference at the metal level.</p>
						<div class="step-resources">
							<span class="resource-link">→ llama.cpp, axolotl</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="path-arrow">→</div>

					<div class="path-step">
						<div class="step-icon">🤖</div>
						<h3>03 // BUILD</h3>
						<p>Move beyond simple prompts. Build agents that can reason, plan, and execute. Context is everything.</p>
						<div class="step-resources">
							<span class="resource-link">→ Crucible</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="path-arrow">→</div>

					<div class="path-step">
						<div class="step-icon">🚀</div>
						<h3>04 // SHIP</h3>
						<p>Build AI-native applications. Eat your own dog food. Create tools your team actually uses.</p>
						<div class="step-resources">
							<span class="resource-link">→ Risk Analysis, Code Review</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="why" class="section why-it-matters">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<span class="section-label">> SECTION_03</span>
					<h2>WHY THIS MATTERS</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="why-grid">
					<div class="why-item">
						<span class="why-stat">↓</span>
						<h4>NO MORE BLACK BOXES</h4>
						<p>Understand what's happening under the hood. Debug when things break.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="why-item">
						<span class="why-stat">↑</span>
						<h4>BETTER OUTPUTS</h4>
						<p>Fine tuning and context engineering produce far better results than better prompts.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="why-item">
						<span class="why-stat">🔒</span>
						<h4>DATA STAYS LOCAL</h4>
						<p>Run models on your own infrastructure. No data leaves your environment.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="why-item">
						<span class="why-stat">⚡</span>
						<h4>FASTER & CHEAPER</h4>
						<p>Small fine-tuned models outperform large APIs at a fraction of the cost.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section cta">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="cta-box">
					<div class="cta-header">> READY_TO_BUILD?</div>
					<h2>START BUILDING</h2>
					<p>Head to the fundamentals tutorial to begin. Or explore the repos to see how these pieces fit together.</p>
					<div class="cta-buttons">
						<a href="https://github.com/irbull/ai-the-hard-way" class="btn btn-primary">$ LLMS_THE_HARD_WAY</a>
						<a href="https://github.com/irbull/crucible" class="btn btn-secondary">$ CRUCIBLE</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<footer class="footer">
		<div class="container">
			<pre class="ascii-art">
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  (c) 2026 VibeDecoding                     │
│  Built by a pragmatist, for pragmatists    │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────┘
			</pre>
		</div>
	</footer>
</Layout>

<style>
	:root {
		--color-bg: #fafafa;
		--color-surface: #ffffff;
		--color-text: #1a1a1a;
		--color-text-dim: #666666;
		--color-text-muted: #888888;
		--color-primary: #6366f1;
		--color-primary-hover: #818cf8;
		--color-secondary: #0891b2;
		--color-accent: #f59e0b;
		--color-border: #e5e5e5;
		--color-terminal-bg: #1a1a1a;
	}

	.header {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		background: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.9);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		z-index: 100;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.nav {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.logo {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--color-text);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.prompt {
		color: var(--color-primary);
		margin-right: 0.5rem;
	}

	.nav-links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.nav-links a {
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 500;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.nav-links a:hover {
		color: var(--color-primary);
	}

	.hero {
		padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: center;
		min-height: 80vh;
	}

	.hero-badge {
		display: inline-block;
		background: var(--color-border);
		color: var(--color-text-dim);
		padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		border-radius: 2px;
	}

	.hero h1 {
		font-size: 2.75rem;
		line-height: 1.1;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
		color: var(--color-text);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.gradient-text {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-secondary) 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.hero-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.hero-cta {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 2px;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		transition: all 0.2s;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: var(--color-primary);
		color: white;
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		background: var(--color-primary-hover);
	}

	.btn-secondary {
		background: transparent;
		color: var(--color-text);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.btn-secondary:hover {
		border-color: var(--color-primary);
		color: var(--color-primary);
	}

	.hero-visual {
		position: relative;
	}

	.terminal {
		background: var(--color-terminal-bg);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		border-radius: 6px;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
	}

	.terminal-header {
		background: var(--color-surface);
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.terminal-dots {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.25rem;
		font-size: 0.5rem;
	}

	.terminal-dots::before {
		content: "● ● ●";
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
	}

	.terminal-title {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
	}

	.terminal-body {
		padding: 1rem;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
	}

	.terminal-line {
		margin: 0.25rem 0;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
	}

	.terminal-cursor {
		color: var(--color-primary);
		animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
	}

	@keyframes blink {
		0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
		50% { opacity: 0; }
	}

	.section {
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		border-top: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.section-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.section-label {
		display: block;
		color: var(--color-secondary);
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.section h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--color-text);
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
	}

	.section-intro {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto 3rem;
	}

	.pillars {
		background: var(--color-surface);
	}

	.pillars-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.pillar-card {
		background: var(--color-bg);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.pillar-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.pillar-number {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-secondary);
	}

	.pillar-header h3 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.pillar-card p {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		line-height: 1.5;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.pillar-tags {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.tag {
		font-size: 0.65rem;
		padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
		background: var(--color-border);
		border-radius: 2px;
		color: var(--color-text-dim);
	}

	.pillar-links a {
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		color: var(--color-primary);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.path {
		background: var(--color-bg);
	}

	.path-flow {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.path-step {
		flex: 1;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--color-surface);
		border-radius: 4px;
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.step-icon {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.path-step h3 {
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--color-text);
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	.path-step p {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.step-resources {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--color-secondary);
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.path-arrow {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--color-border);
		padding-top: 3rem;
	}

	.why-it-matters {
		background: var(--color-surface);
	}

	.why-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.why-item {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		border-radius: 4px;
		background: var(--color-bg);
	}

	.why-stat {
		display: block;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-primary);
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.why-item h4 {
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
		color: var(--color-text);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	.why-item p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		font-size: 0.8rem;
	}

	.cta {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-surface) 0%, var(--color-bg) 100%);
	}

	.cta-header {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--color-secondary);
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.cta h2 {
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.cta-box {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.cta-box p {
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		font-size: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.cta .btn-primary {
		background: var(--color-text);
		color: var(--color-bg);
	}

	.cta .btn-secondary {
		border: 1px solid var(--color-primary);
		color: var(--color-primary);
	}

	.footer {
		background: var(--color-bg);
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		padding: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		border-top: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
	}

	.footer p {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.ascii-art {
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
		color: var(--color-text-dim);
		margin: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.path-flow {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
		.path-arrow {
			transform: rotate(90deg);
			padding: 0;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			padding-top: 6rem;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.hero-cta {
			justify-content: center;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
		}

		.hero-visual {
			display: none;
		}

		.pillars-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.why-grid {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		}

		.nav-links {
			display: none;
		}

		.cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}
	}
</style>
